sentence: Among the underlying components of the S&P 500 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Vulcan Materials Co (Symbol: VMC), where a total of 9,531 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 953,100 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 102.1% of VMC's average daily trading volume over the past month of 933,550 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $145 strike put option expiring October 18, 2019, with 3,012 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 301,200 underlying shares of VMC.
